Player born in Valencia on January 2, 1997. He started in football as a child in the land fields of Bonrep√≥s. 
When he was only 7 years old, he joined the Valencia CF Academy. He moved up through the academy quickly, varying 
his initial position as a striker, scoring more than 500 goals, and finally ending up as a midfielder. He debuted 
